However, I can in my mind create a girl next door fantasy around her not being in super-model shape, so that fits with my project. Also, and what I was hoping to see in this video, you do have to hunt around for them, but there are definitely scenes of her legs open, so a guy can see her vagina and anus. Bottom line, that was what I wanted and it is shown in this video. She also has, not large but cute breasts, and they get quality view time. I also like how young she is. I don't enjoy hardcore porn and cannot use it for masturbation because I don't find it sexually stimulating to watch other people having sex. What I really needed was a movie of a nude woman moving her body, with open crotch views included, and this video does offer all of this, so my requirements have been met. I guess I'm knocking off one star just because I wish there was even more time with the camera staying focused on her behind and open crotch, but like I said, there's enough of the good stuff to meet my masturbation needs.

I picked this up at the free Gym DVD library. I was expecting to at least follow some of the exercises but she doesn't say a thing nor tell us how to stretch out. Also, I did not know that nudity helped in any of the exercises. This was a waste. My Gym partner, who weighs 500lbs, didn't get anything out of this either except a craving for hot dogs.

Great video of a beautiful woman sweating, jumping, exercising in the nude.  Follow along with the program or just sit back and watch; she will get your blood pumping.  Tatyana is natural, no fake here.  Certainly not pornographic, just a cute blond exercising and sweating in the nude.  She does lack enthusiasm, but she is cute, blond, and naked.

I too was attracted by the packaging as I'm an admirer of athletic women.  But this DVD seems pointless.

The model ia a young rather plain peroxide blond who is completely shaved and who goes through a series of exercises on a variety of exercise machines.

But there is no emotion or even personality shown and the overall feeling is mechanical and unattractive.  There are several brief closeups of her shaved mound and of her small breasts but the DVD is neither entertaining nor erotic.

I regret spending my money on this.

I have read other reviews of this and I must say it is pretty tame stuff.  Anybody who thinks there is anything that is pornographic doesn't know what pornography is.  This is pretty tame stuff.  Other than a few very short closeups down under, this could easily be on cable TV.  I expected something more revealing.

Tatyana is an average looking 20 something woman.  Nothing fake but nothing noteworthy either.  If you are considering this for the exercise value you will be disappointed.  If you are considering it for eye candy, it is middle of the road.

nude blonde exercising...ok!
close ups of the shaven sweet spots give it 3 star rating [deducting 2 star for being shaved]...

light-hearted fun!

If you're looking for explicit content its not here.  if you are looking for a workout DVD to follow with a naked instructor you won't find it here.  If you've ever watched an attractive woman at a gym and wondered what she looked like with nothing on - this is for you.  Its very cut and dry.  She gets undressed and works out.  Plenty of close-ups, but nothing obscene.

I was only able to locate and purchase this item on amazon.com, Thanks once again for helping to find this hard to find item it was a great product and service, A+++ Highly recommended to devoted fans!
